{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1228,"text":"In many patriarchal societies and tribal societies,"},{"time":5262,"text":"fathers are usually known by their sons,"},{"time":10487,"text":"but I'm one of the few fathers"},{"time":13703,"text":"who is known by his daughter,"},{"time":15747,"text":"and I am proud of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17373,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23810,"text":"Malala started her campaign for education"},{"time":26658,"text":"and stood for her rights in 2007,"},{"time":29545,"text":"and when her efforts were honored in 2011,"},{"time":34103,"text":"and she was given the national youth peace prize,"},{"time":37543,"text":"and she became a very famous,"},{"time":39412,"text":"very popular young girl of her country."},{"time":43456,"text":"Before that, she was my daughter,"},{"time":46784,"text":"but now I am her father."},{"time":50741,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":52496,"text":"if we glance to human history,"},{"time":55643,"text":"the story of women"},{"time":58471,"text":"is the story of injustice,"},{"time":61847,"text":"inequality,"},{"time":63907,"text":"violence and exploitation."},{"time":69218,"text":"You see,"},{"time":71053,"text":"in patriarchal societies,"},{"time":75204,"text":"right from the very beginning,"},{"time":77646,"text":"when a girl is born,"},{"time":80652,"text":"her birth is not celebrated."},{"time":84932,"text":"She is not welcomed,"},{"time":87096,"text":"neither by father nor by mother."},{"time":89872,"text":"The neighborhood comes"},{"time":91557,"text":"and commiserates with the mother,"},{"time":94058,"text":"and nobody congratulates the father."},{"time":99152,"text":"And a mother is very uncomfortable"},{"time":103467,"text":"for having a girl child."},{"time":107834,"text":"When she gives birth to the first girl child,"},{"time":111094,"text":"first daughter, she is sad."},{"time":115183,"text":"When she gives birth to the second daughter,"},{"time":118930,"text":"she is shocked,"},{"time":120777,"text":"and in the expectation of a son,"},{"time":124161,"text":"when she gives birth to a third daughter,"},{"time":127367,"text":"she feels guilty like a criminal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132906,"text":"Not only the mother suffers,"},{"time":135540,"text":"but the daughter, the newly born daughter,"},{"time":138277,"text":"when she grows old,"},{"time":140412,"text":"she suffers too."},{"time":142547,"text":"At the age of five,"},{"time":144600,"text":"while she should be going to school,"},{"time":147929,"text":"she stays at home"},{"time":149672,"text":"and her brothers are admitted in a school."},{"time":154294,"text":"Until the age of 12, somehow,"},{"time":156887,"text":"she has a good life."},{"time":159528,"text":"She can have fun."},{"time":161199,"text":"She can play with her friends in the streets,"},{"time":164388,"text":"and she can move around in the streets"},{"time":166427,"text":"like a butterfly."},{"time":169202,"text":"But when she enters her teens,"},{"time":173017,"text":"when she becomes 13 years old,"},{"time":175357,"text":"she is forbidden to go out of her home"},{"time":178976,"text":"without a male escort."},{"time":182468,"text":"She is confined under the four walls of her home."},{"time":187843,"text":"She is no more a free individual."},{"time":193037,"text":"She becomes the so-called honor"},{"time":196057,"text":"of her father and of her brothers"},{"time":198538,"text":"and of her family,"},{"time":201988,"text":"and if she transgresses"},{"time":204676,"text":"the code of that so-called honor,"},{"time":207887,"text":"she could even be killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212251,"text":"And it is also interesting that this so-called"},{"time":216252,"text":"code of honor,"},{"time":217615,"text":"it does not only affect the life of a girl,"},{"time":221305,"text":"it also affects the life"},{"time":223431,"text":"of the male members of the family."},{"time":228230,"text":"I know a family of seven sisters and one brother,"},{"time":234823,"text":"and that one brother,"},{"time":236645,"text":"he has migrated to the Gulf countries,"},{"time":240149,"text":"to earn a living for his seven sisters"},{"time":242844,"text":"and parents,"},{"time":245192,"text":"because he thinks that it will be humiliating"},{"time":251046,"text":"if his seven sisters learn a skill"},{"time":253768,"text":"and they go out of the home"},{"time":256148,"text":"and earn some livelihood."},{"time":260299,"text":"So this brother,"},{"time":261889,"text":"he sacrifices the joys of his life"},{"time":265242,"text":"and the happiness of his sisters"},{"time":268634,"text":"at the altar of so-called honor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273218,"text":"And there is one more norm"},{"time":274752,"text":"of the patriarchal societies"},{"time":277110,"text":"that is called obedience."},{"time":281560,"text":"A good girl is supposed to be"},{"time":285346,"text":"very quiet, very humble"},{"time":290594,"text":"and very submissive."},{"time":294565,"text":"It is the criteria."},{"time":295904,"text":"The role model good girl should be very quiet."},{"time":299736,"text":"She is supposed to be silent"},{"time":302025,"text":"and she is supposed to accept the decisions"},{"time":305196,"text":"of her father and mother"},{"time":307416,"text":"and the decisions of elders,"},{"time":310641,"text":"even if she does not like them."},{"time":313047,"text":"If she is married to a man she doesn't like"},{"time":316376,"text":"or if she is married to an old man,"},{"time":319118,"text":"she has to accept,"},{"time":320678,"text":"because she does not want to be dubbed"},{"time":323196,"text":"as disobedient."},{"time":325819,"text":"If she is married very early,"},{"time":327451,"text":"she has to accept."},{"time":328925,"text":"Otherwise, she will be called disobedient."},{"time":332947,"text":"And what happens at the end?"},{"time":335750,"text":"In the words of a poetess,"},{"time":337505,"text":"she is wedded, bedded,"},{"time":340292,"text":"and then she gives birth\nto more sons and daughters."},{"time":345463,"text":"And it is the irony of the situation"},{"time":348232,"text":"that this mother,"},{"time":350564,"text":"she teaches the same lesson of obedience"},{"time":353616,"text":"to her daughter"},{"time":354676,"text":"and the same lesson of honor to her sons."},{"time":359109,"text":"And this vicious cycle goes on, goes on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365997,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":368524,"text":"this plight of millions of women"},{"time":371746,"text":"could be changed"},{"time":374578,"text":"if we think differently,"},{"time":376953,"text":"if women and men think differently,"},{"time":380934,"text":"if men and women in the\ntribal and patriarchal societies"},{"time":385152,"text":"in the developing countries,"},{"time":387135,"text":"if they can break a few norms"},{"time":390046,"text":"of family and society,"},{"time":394650,"text":"if they can abolish the discriminatory laws"},{"time":400130,"text":"of the systems in their states,"},{"time":402658,"text":"which go against the basic human rights"},{"time":404949,"text":"of the women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408743,"text":"Dear brothers and sisters, when Malala was born,"},{"time":413987,"text":"and for the first time,"},{"time":416140,"text":"believe me,"},{"time":417414,"text":"I don't like newborn children, to be honest,"},{"time":422391,"text":"but when I went and I looked into her eyes,"},{"time":426173,"text":"believe me,"},{"time":428293,"text":"I got extremely honored."},{"time":432274,"text":"And long before she was born,"},{"time":434444,"text":"I thought about her name,"},{"time":437480,"text":"and I was fascinated with a heroic"},{"time":440765,"text":"legendary freedom fighter in Afghanistan."},{"time":444630,"text":"Her name was Malalai of Maiwand,"},{"time":449639,"text":"and I named my daughter after her."},{"time":453924,"text":"A few days after Malala was born,"},{"time":456916,"text":"my daughter was born,"},{"time":458655,"text":"my cousin came --"},{"time":460313,"text":"and it was a coincidence --"},{"time":462281,"text":"he came to my home"},{"time":464996,"text":"and he brought a family tree,"},{"time":467701,"text":"a family tree of the Yousafzai family,"},{"time":471369,"text":"and when I looked at the family tree,"},{"time":473925,"text":"it traced back to 300 years of our ancestors."},{"time":479978,"text":"But when I looked, all were men,"},{"time":484375,"text":"and I picked my pen,"},{"time":486797,"text":"drew a line from my name,"},{"time":488801,"text":"and wrote, \"Malala.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":493585,"text":"And when she grow old,"},{"time":496355,"text":"when she was four and a half years old,"},{"time":499938,"text":"I admitted her in my school."},{"time":503474,"text":"You will be asking, then, why should I mention about"},{"time":506380,"text":"the admission of a girl in a school?"},{"time":508882,"text":"Yes, I must mention it."},{"time":510937,"text":"It may be taken for granted in Canada,"},{"time":514022,"text":"in America, in many developed countries,"},{"time":517849,"text":"but in poor countries,"},{"time":520307,"text":"in patriarchal societies, in tribal societies,"},{"time":523875,"text":"it's a big event for the life of girl."},{"time":527489,"text":"Enrollment in a school means"},{"time":531128,"text":"recognition of her identity and her name."},{"time":536877,"text":"Admission in a school means"},{"time":538555,"text":"that she has entered the world of dreams"},{"time":542237,"text":"and aspirations"},{"time":543900,"text":"where she can explore her potentials"},{"time":547412,"text":"for her future life."},{"time":550658,"text":"I have five sisters,"},{"time":552737,"text":"and none of them could go to school,"},{"time":556051,"text":"and you will be astonished,"},{"time":557625,"text":"two weeks before,"},{"time":561735,"text":"when I was filling out the Canadian visa form,"},{"time":566018,"text":"and I was filling out the family part of the form,"},{"time":570683,"text":"I could not recall"},{"time":572767,"text":"the surnames of some of my sisters."},{"time":576772,"text":"And the reason was"},{"time":578621,"text":"that I have never, never seen the names"},{"time":581913,"text":"of my sisters written on any document."},{"time":587739,"text":"That was the reason that"},{"time":590679,"text":"I valued my daughter."},{"time":594212,"text":"What my father could not give to my sisters"},{"time":598525,"text":"and to his daughters,"},{"time":600280,"text":"I thought I must change it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604521,"text":"I used to appreciate the intelligence"},{"time":607528,"text":"and the brilliance of my daughter."},{"time":611200,"text":"I encouraged her to sit with me"},{"time":613794,"text":"when my friends used to come."},{"time":615453,"text":"I encouraged her to go with\nme to different meetings."},{"time":620237,"text":"And all these good values,"},{"time":621898,"text":"I tried to inculcate in her personality."},{"time":625108,"text":"And this was not only she, only Malala."},{"time":628771,"text":"I imparted all these good values"},{"time":631507,"text":"to my school, girl students \nand boy students as well."},{"time":636050,"text":"I used education for emancipation."},{"time":640429,"text":"I taught my girls,"},{"time":642294,"text":"I taught my girl students,"},{"time":644249,"text":"to unlearn the lesson of obedience."},{"time":649318,"text":"I taught my boy students"},{"time":652283,"text":"to unlearn the lesson of so-called pseudo-honor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661696,"text":"Dear brothers and sisters,"},{"time":665681,"text":"we were striving for more rights for women,"},{"time":670264,"text":"and we were struggling to have more,"},{"time":673886,"text":"more and more space for the women in society."},{"time":678113,"text":"But we came across a new phenomenon."},{"time":681326,"text":"It was lethal to human rights"},{"time":683819,"text":"and particularly to women's rights."},{"time":687267,"text":"It was called Talibanization."},{"time":691944,"text":"It means a complete negation"},{"time":695632,"text":"of women's participation"},{"time":697842,"text":"in all political, economical and social activities."},{"time":704037,"text":"Hundreds of schools were lost."},{"time":707584,"text":"Girls were prohibited from going to school."},{"time":713815,"text":"Women were forced to wear veils"},{"time":717521,"text":"and they were stopped from going to the markets."},{"time":721077,"text":"Musicians were silenced,"},{"time":723661,"text":"girls were flogged"},{"time":725618,"text":"and singers were killed."},{"time":729101,"text":"Millions were suffering,"},{"time":730975,"text":"but few spoke,"},{"time":734220,"text":"and it was the most scary thing"},{"time":736444,"text":"when you have all around such people"},{"time":742530,"text":"who kill and who flog,"},{"time":744556,"text":"and you speak for your rights."},{"time":745852,"text":"It's really the most scary thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":750059,"text":"At the age of 10,"},{"time":751952,"text":"Malala stood, and she stood for the right"},{"time":756196,"text":"of education."},{"time":758507,"text":"She wrote a diary for the BBC blog,"},{"time":763279,"text":"she volunteered herself"},{"time":765483,"text":"for the New York Times documentaries,"},{"time":769077,"text":"and she spoke from every platform she could."},{"time":773993,"text":"And her voice was the most powerful voice."},{"time":778381,"text":"It spread like a crescendo all around the world."},{"time":784634,"text":"And that was the reason the Taliban"},{"time":786486,"text":"could not tolerate her campaign,"},{"time":790817,"text":"and on October 9 2012,"},{"time":793666,"text":"she was shot in the head at point blank range."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799415,"text":"It was a doomsday for my family and for me."},{"time":803560,"text":"The world turned into a big black hole."},{"time":809379,"text":"While my daughter was"},{"time":811045,"text":"on the verge of life and death,"},{"time":814497,"text":"I whispered into the ears of my wife,"},{"time":818336,"text":"\"Should I be blamed for what happened"},{"time":821438,"text":"to my daughter and your daughter?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":825114,"text":"And she abruptly told me,"},{"time":827635,"text":"\"Please don't blame yourself."},{"time":830146,"text":"You stood for the right cause."},{"time":833362,"text":"You put your life at stake"},{"time":835497,"text":"for the cause of truth,"},{"time":836900,"text":"for the cause of peace,"},{"time":838081,"text":"and for the cause of education,"},{"time":840189,"text":"and your daughter in inspired from you"},{"time":842238,"text":"and she joined you."},{"time":844469,"text":"You both were on the right path"},{"time":846144,"text":"and God will protect her.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":849517,"text":"These few words meant a lot to me,"},{"time":852863,"text":"and I didn't ask this question again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":856974,"text":"When Malala was in the hospital,"},{"time":861094,"text":"and she was going through the severe pains"},{"time":864341,"text":"and she had had severe headaches"},{"time":866861,"text":"because her facial nerve was cut down,"},{"time":870049,"text":"I used to see a dark shadow"},{"time":872501,"text":"spreading on the face of my wife."},{"time":878038,"text":"But my daughter never complained."},{"time":884139,"text":"She used to tell us,"},{"time":886200,"text":"\"I'm fine with my crooked smile"},{"time":888251,"text":"and with my numbness in my face."},{"time":890993,"text":"I'll be okay. Please don't worry.\""},{"time":893072,"text":"She was a solace for us,"},{"time":895201,"text":"and she consoled us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900120,"text":"Dear brothers and sisters,"},{"time":904341,"text":"we learned from her how to be resilient"},{"time":906963,"text":"in the most difficult times,"},{"time":910268,"text":"and I'm glad to share with you"},{"time":913276,"text":"that despite being an icon"},{"time":919168,"text":"for the rights of children and women,"},{"time":921997,"text":"she is like any 16-year old girl."},{"time":927290,"text":"She cries when her homework is incomplete."},{"time":932422,"text":"She quarrels with her brothers,"},{"time":934490,"text":"and I am very happy for that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":938213,"text":"People ask me,"},{"time":940616,"text":"what special is in my mentorship"},{"time":944108,"text":"which has made Malala so bold"},{"time":946648,"text":"and so courageous and so vocal and poised?"},{"time":951140,"text":"I tell them, don't ask me what I did."},{"time":957415,"text":"Ask me what I did not do."},{"time":961276,"text":"I did not clip her wings, and that's all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":966533,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":969415,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":974911,"text":"Thank you. Thank you very much. Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}